DESCRIPTION:Join us to learn the steps to home ownership and the resources 
	that help pave the way! During part one\\\, we’ll cover the home buying pr
	ocess and best practices using recently sold homes as examples. Plus\\\, a
	n informative Q&A with a home inspector. During part two\\\, we’ll dive de
	eper into available downpayment assistance (DPA) programs. You’re welcome 
	to attend part one or both sessions. \\nWe meet at 6pm in the Phinney Cent
	er\\\, Blue Building. Snacks and NA drinks provided. Please RSVP at caitli
	n.lakere.com.\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/homebuyer-workshops-2
